# Glico app v3 — Vue 3 + Element Plus (codebase dich migrate)

**Pham vi:** Lam viec trong **`glico-app-v3`**. Co the **doi chieu** file tuong ung o **`glico-app-v2`** khi port, nhung **output** luon la code **Vue 3 + Element Plus + Pinia + Router 4** trong **v3**.

**Ban chat:** **Migrate / port ky thuat** tu Vue 2 + Element UI sang **Vue 3 + Element Plus**. **Luong man hinh, quy trinh nghiep vu, dieu kien, thu tu goi API, payload, validation, hanh vi nguoi dung** — **giu nguyen nhu ban v2**; khong doi de "cai thien" hay refactor nghiep vu.

## Nguyen tac

1. **Khong doi logic / luong nghiep vu:** dieu kien, luong xu ly, man hinh tiep theo, goi API, payload, tham so — **giong hanh vi v2**; chi doi **cu phap & API thu vien** (Vue 3, Element Plus, Pinia, Router, v.v.) khi bat buoc.
2. **Khong doi CSS / giao dien:** **khong** sua selector, mau, kich thuoc, margin/padding, class style — **khong** doi `<style>` tru **mot ngoai le:** **`/deep/`** → `::v-deep` / **`:deep()`** khi **build bao loi**.
3. **Chi sua khi** build/runtime **loi** hoac **bat buoc** Vue 3 / Element Plus — khong refactor thua.
4. **Giu** Options API, ten bien/ham — **khong** tach component neu khong bat buoc.
5. **Entry v3** (`main.ts`/`main.js`, router, Pinia): cau hinh **mot lan** cho project; **moi file `.vue` trong v3** chi sua noi dung trong file do.

## Vue 3 trong `.vue`

- **Filter** (`|`) → method / computed (**ket qua hien thi giong v2**).
- **`slot-scope` / `slot=`** → `#` / `v-slot`.
- **`$listeners`** → gop `$attrs` khi can / khi loi.
- **`/deep/`** → `::v-deep` / **`:deep()`** **chi khi** build loi — **khong** sua rule CSS khac.
- **Component + `v-model`:** neu loi → `modelValue` / `update:modelValue` (Vue 3).

**Global filter:** khong dung `Vue.filter` tren Vue 3 — chuyen sang ham / `globalProperties` neu can, **cung ket qua** nhu v2.

## Element UI (v2) → Element Plus (v3)

| Element UI | Element Plus |
|------------|--------------|
| `size="medium"` | `size="default"` |
| `size="mini"` | `size="small"` |
| `<el-submenu>` | `<el-sub-menu>` |
| `<i class="el-icon-xxx">` | `<el-icon><Xxx /></el-icon>` + `@element-plus/icons-vue` |
| Khac | Chi khi loi build hoac tai lieu EP |

**Entry v3:** `ElMessage`, `ElMessageBox`, … (import tu `element-plus`), thay prototype Element UI v2.

## Pinia — module `common` (tuong ung Vuex v2)

Giu ten **`isLoading`**, **`setLoading`**:

```javascript
import { mapState, mapActions } from 'pinia'
import { useCommonStore } from '@/stores/common'

export default {
  computed: { ...mapState(useCommonStore, ['isLoading']) },
  methods: { ...mapActions(useCommonStore, ['setLoading']) },
}
```

## Khung app v3 (tom tat)

- **Vue Router 4** + **Pinia** (khong dung `vue-router@3` / `vuex@3`).
- **Ant Design Vue 4.x** neu project con dung; trong tung file chi sua khi loi, giu hanh vi.
- **vue-i18n:** uu tien locale Nhat cho Element Plus; bo khoi entry neu khong dung `$t`.

